Definition: slightly succulent perennial with basal leaves and hairy sticky stems each bearing a solitary flower head with narrow pink or lavender rays
Example: coastal bluffs Oregon to southern California
Synonyms: beach_aster, Erigeron_glaucous, fleabane, slightly, succulent, perennial, with, basal, leaves, and, hairy, sticky, stems, each, bearing, a, solitary, flower, head, narrow, pink, or, lavender, rays, coastal, bluffs, Oregon, to, southern, California
Category: noun.plant
